# ── web/model.onnx — INCLUDE this (needed for GitHub Pages) ───
# model.onnx is NOT ignored — it must be in the repo for the
# web app to work. It will be ~5–15MB which is fine for GitHub.
# If it exceeds 50MB, use Git LFS (instructions in README).